      "requiredLevel": 2,
      "achievedLevel": 2,
      "factorStatus": "assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Predicted normalized index of hemolysis (NIH) must agree with experimental values within 20% across all 5 operating points.",
      "rationale": "Predicted NIH values agreed with experimental measurements within 14% across all 5 flow-speed combinations. The RH acceptance criterion (RH < 1) was satisfied at all operating points. Required level 2 is met."
    },
    {
