    "actor": "https://uofa.net/synth/actor/morrison-credibility-team",
    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All seven assessed credibility factors meet or exceed required levels for MRL 2. The six non-assessed factors are acceptable at MRL 2 per the ASME V&V 40 framework. Monte Carlo UQ has been performed and confirms that output NIH uncertainty is within the 20% acceptance band. The RH < 1 criterion is satisfied across all five operating points. The assessment team notes that sensitivity analysis identifying dominant input drivers has not yet been completed and is planned for a future revision, but this does not preclude acceptance at the current MRL 2 assurance level.",
